headline: Gerald Johnson elected to Eaton’s Board of Directors
summary: DUBLIN, July 23, 2025--Intelligent power management company Eaton (NYSE:ETN) today announced that Gerald Johnson has been elected to the company’s Board of Directors effective July 23, 2025.

headline: Eaton declares quarterly dividend payable August 22, 2025
summary: DUBLIN, July 23, 2025--The Board of Directors of intelligent power management company Eaton (NYSE:ETN) today declared a quarterly dividend of $1.04 per ordinary share. The dividend is payable August 22, 2025, to shareholders of record at the close of business on August 7, 2025. Eaton has paid dividends on its shares every year since 1923.
